{"tid":170453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]熱狗仔隊:三月七日起,發現有可疑人士監視曾俊華行蹤","createTime":"2017-03-24T17:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T02:46:50.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc787acc12077e46239816a73e87fe435ac2437","tid":170453,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"【獨家報道 解放軍全程監視曾俊華 萬人集會驚動中共？】<br />\n本報熱狗仔隊經多日追蹤調查，由三月七日起，發現有可疑人士監視曾俊華行蹤，於三月十八日，曾俊華當日落區宣傳，本報狗仔隊由大圍開始，於荃灣及尖沙咀發現三名可疑人士監控曾俊華的宣傳活動，途中發現其中一可疑人士操不純正廣東話，於曾俊華離開柏麗大道現場後，三人從不同方面離開，失去蹤影。於今日（三\u001d月二十四日）本報熱狗仔隊跟蹤曾俊華的宣傳活動，亦發現有多名可疑人士監控曾俊華的宣傳活動，發現幾名可疑人士最終返回中國人民解放軍駐香港部隊大廈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1408045732591923/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2F1408045732591923%2F&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=246836fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1408045732591923/</a>"},{"pid":"69b970126462486be2e24d41500c3e68f0130fa9","tid":170453,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fe522f18cfa50930cdf56d78682a9c369a2c0c","tid":170453,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"共產黨又放料比熱狗時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c56ceb44ae36f1e37de8dc9903c8cba70184632","tid":170453,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47143b0f09b93c2a33c8135fb65303c2f099f39a","tid":170453,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"關我鳩事咩，邊個選咪又一鳩樣"},{"pid